_sText: This map is an extended version of valves de_dust. The reason i did this was because valves dust gave a campfest and didnt support enough players. Because i extended the map it now easily handles 64 players while allowing the T's to plant the bomb often enough also. The map has working overviews and a nav file. The following features are added: - A side route above the bridge. - A sewer leading to a garage in site A. - The sewer also has an exit inside a buildings between site A and B. - A side route at the bridge (sewer also ends here). - A side route in the temple. - And some tiny gameplay changes. - Redone HDR Note: Since the map is extended lower player counts could give some unbalance or make the map feel empty Map is done by me (Alias |UKCS|) Overview is done by Nelsaidi (aka. LG |UKCS|) Beta testing is supported by UKCS (special thanks to TC and LD for making it possible)
